Entities.Name: APInvoice
Entities.Description: Primary Invoice Fields used in 2-Way Match Account Payable Invoice Automation Solution Accelerator

Fields.Name: PONumber
Fields.Description: PO Number resulted after the PO Matching step (or PO Number to use if the Matching is skipped)

Fields.Name: ExtractedPONumber
Fields.Description: PO Number extracted by the DU Process

Fields.Name: InternalFASystemID
Fields.Description: The ID of the Invoice once added in the internal F&A application (e.g. Coupa)

Fields.Name: Status
Fields.Description: Represents the processing status of the Invoice Record. New values can be added through the InvoiceStatus choice set.

Fields.Name: Source
Fields.Description: Should represent the source where the invoice was retrieved from. By Default this can be  Email, SharedDrive but more values can be added in the Source ChoiceSet.

Entities.Name: APInvoiceLineItem
Entities.Description: Line Items in Invoice Table used in 2-Way Match Account Payable Invoice Automation Solution Accelerator

Fields.Name: Quantity
Fields.Description: This field should be used in relation with the UnitPrice Field

Fields.Name: TotalAmount
Fields.Description: Can either represent the Amount of a non quantity Line Item OR the total between Unit Amount * Quanitity

Fields.Name: LinePONumber
Fields.Description: Number of the corresponding PO Line

Fields.Name: UnitPrice
Fields.Description: This field should be used in relation with the Quantity Field

Fields.Name: Invoice
Fields.Description: The Parent Invoice this line item belongs to

Fields.Name: SenderName
Fields.Description: The name of the packing list sender

Fields.Name: ReceiverName
Fields.Description: The name of the packing list receiver

Fields.Name: OrderNumber
Fields.Description: The order number of the packing list

Fields.Name: PONumber
Fields.Description: The PO Number of the packing list

Fields.Name: TotalQuantityShipped
Fields.Description: The total Quantity Shipped in the packing list

Fields.Name: TotalQuantityOrdered
Fields.Description: The total Quantity Ordered in the packing list

Fields.Name: DocumentDate
Fields.Description: The document date of the packing list

Fields.Name: Status
Fields.Description: Represents the processing status of the Packing List Record. New values can be added through the Packing List status choice set.

Fields.Name: Source
Fields.Description: Should represent the source where the Packing List was retrieved from. By Default this can be Email, SharedDrive but more values can be added in the Packing List Source ChoiceSet.

Fields.Name: Code
Fields.Description: Line Item Code, could also be the PO Item

Fields.Name: PackingList
Fields.Description: The packing list that this entity is related to

Entities.Name: ProjectTestCaseDetail

Entities.Name: ProjectTestExecutions
Entities.Description: Contains Test Execution details of the Testing Project in the Organization

Entities.Name: ProjectTestSetDetails
Entities.Description: Contains Test details of the Testing Project in the Organization

Entities.Name: SAPCreateOrderOrgData
Entities.Description: Organizational data for creating SAP orders

Entities.Name: SAPPOHEADER
Entities.Description: PO Header entity used in BAPI_PO_CREATE

Fields.Name: VENDOR
Fields.Description: Number of the vendor or supplier

Fields.Name: DELIVDATE
Fields.Description: Delivery Date (Scheduled date for the line)

Fields.Name: PURMAT
Fields.Description: Material Number Used by the Vendor

Entities.Name: SAPTestDataList
Entities.Description: Used in SAP Test Data Management app

Entities.Name: StudioWebSAPUI5
Entities.Description: Data service entity for Studio Web workflow working with SAP UI5 application environment

Entities.Name: SystemUser
Entities.Description: Contains Automation Cloud users and groups that have ever had roles assigned, or accessed Data Service

Entities.Name: TSAppTestingSlides
Entities.DisplayName: Test Suite Demo App - App Testing Slides
